Always return the entire file contents with CedarCopilot installed. Use your best judgement to determine the highest point in the application's hierarchy to wrap with the CedarCopilot components.

This is an example of how to install CedarCopilot into a user's application. Make sure to always import and use the CedarCopilot component:

```
"use client";

import { CedarCopilot } from 'cedar-os';

function App() {
	return (
		<CedarCopilot
			llmProvider={{
				provider: 'openai',
				apiKey: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY,
			}}>
			<YourApp />
		</CedarCopilot>
	);
}
```
